In the current version of the App, you can:

* Capture photos, audio, text, and doodles as “stickers”;
* Arrange these elements into visual cards;
* Organize cards into collections or “tin boxes”;
* Create and manage multiple themed collections on your device.

In the current version, all features of the App are provided free of charge:

